\par\pard\plain \tx0\sa120\sb120\ltrch\loch {\f7\fs22\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Ps::7>[ Evan's final acceptance that his relationship with Sarah is over somehow resulted in a feeling of peace. His emotional status transitioned from hurt, anger, and upset to feeling nostalgic as his mind fondly returns to the moment of their first kiss.]<!$Scr_Ps::7>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f5\fs26\b1\i0\cf8 <$Scr_Cs::4>Evan<!$Scr_Cs::4>}{\f6\fs26\b0\i1\cf9 <$Scr_Cs::5> (A fond glimmer in his eye with a matching grin):<!$Scr_Cs::5>}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If this is the last time we\u8217\'92re going to see each other, I think we should end the relationship like it started. As I recall, I said, \u8216\'91I feel like I should kiss you.\u8217\'92\u8221\'94}
