\par\pard\plain \tx0\fi360\sa120\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f8\fs26\b0\i0 <$Scr_Cs::5><$Scr_Ps::6>Evan's gaze weakened Sarah's resolve. She did still love him. She remained silent and relented as Evan leaned in, their kissing becoming even more passionate. However, in the midst of her passion fear struck and uncharacteristically, tears began to flow. She pulled away from Evan. She hurriedly made attempts to tuck her blouse back in<!$Scr_Cs::5><!$Scr_Ps::6>}
